    dc:creator "Narita, João P. Z.; De, Gilberto J.; Fernando, Liyanage C. P." ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Two species of Neocypholaelaps from Sri Lanka (Acari: Ameroseiidae), with description of a new species" ;
